FuncDef: This command creates an application QoS policy entry. A flow that matches multiple Application QoS policies (AQP) entries will have multiple AQP entries actions applied. When a conflict occurs for two or more actions, the action from the AQP entry with the lowest numerical value takes precedence.

ParaDef.Info: An integer identifying the AQP entry. Values-1 to 65535.
Mandatory keyword creates the entry. The create keyword requirement can be enabled/disabled in the environment>create context.
